## Password Policy

- Minimum 14 characters
- MFA required
- Password Manager Required

## Logging

- 365-day retention
- SIEM ingestion
- CloudTrail enabled

## Access Control

- Least Privilege
- RBAC
- Quarterly Reviews

## Vulnerability Management

- Critical: 7 days
- High: 30 days
- Medium: 90 days
- Low: As scheduled
